---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="About Us" description="Learn about Moi - digitizing the timeless tradition of மொய் for modern celebrations.">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-24 h-24 mb-6">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="w-20 h-20">
          <defs>
            <linearGradient id="aboutSunGold" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:#FCD34D"/>
              <stop offset="50%" style="stop-color:#F59E0B"/>
              <stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:#D97706"/>
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="aboutRuby" x1="50%" y1="0%" x2="50%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:#F87171"/>
              <stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:#DC2626"/>
            </linearGradient>
          </defs>
          <rect x="8" y="8" width="84" height="84" rx="20" fill="url(#aboutSunGold)"/>
          <path d="M44 8 L44 92 L56 92 L56 8 Z" fill="url(#aboutRuby)"/>
          <path d="M8 44 L92 44 L92 56 L8 56 Z" fill="url(#aboutRuby)"/>
          <path d="M50 44 Q28 44 24 28 Q20 12 36 16 Q52 20 50 44" fill="url(#aboutRuby)"/>
          <path d="M50 44 Q72 44 76 28 Q80 12 64 16 Q48 20 50 44" fill="url(#aboutRuby)"/>
          <circle cx="50" cy="42" r="8" fill="#DC2626"/>
          <circle cx="50" cy="42" r="4" fill="#F87171"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">About Moi</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-base-content/60 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Digitizing the timeless tradition of மொய் for modern celebrations
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Story Section -->
    <div class="prose max-w-none mb-16">
      <h2>Our Story</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>மொய் (Moi)</strong> is a beautiful Tamil tradition where friends and family contribute gifts, usually money, during special occasions like weddings, housewarmings, and birthdays. These contributions are carefully recorded in a register, creating a record of love and support that spans generations.
      </p>
      <p>
        We built Moi to bring this cherished tradition into the digital age. No more lost registers, illegible handwriting, or tedious manual totaling. With Moi, every contribution is captured instantly, accurately, and beautifully.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- What We Do -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">What We Offer</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="p-8 bg-base-200/50 border border-base-300">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 4.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h4.5c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v4.5c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-4.5A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 3.75 9.375v-4.5ZM3.75 14.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h4.5c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v4.5c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-4.5a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125v-4.5ZM13.5 4.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h4.5c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v4.5c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-4.5A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 13.5 9.375v-4.5Z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6.75 6.75h.75v.75h-.75v-.75ZM6.75 16.5h.75v.75h-.75v-.75ZM16.5 6.75h.75v.75h-.75v-.75ZM13.5 13.5h.75v.75h-.75v-.75ZM13.5 19.5h.75v.75h-.75v-.75ZM19.5 13.5h.75v.75h-.75v-.75ZM19.5 19.5h.75v.75h-.75v-.75ZM16.5 16.5h.75v.75h-.75v-.75Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">QR Code Collection</h3>
          <p class="text-base-content/60">
            Generate unique QR codes for your events. Guests scan and log their contributions instantly.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 bg-base-200/50 border border-base-300">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-success/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-success" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12h3.75M9 15h3.75M9 18h3.75m3 .75H18a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25-2.25V6.108c0-1.135-.845-2.098-1.976-2.192a48.424 48.424 0 0 0-1.123-.08m-5.801 0c-.065.21-.1.433-.1.664 0 .414.336.75.75.75h4.5a.75.75 0 0 0 .75-.75 2.25 2.25 0 0 0-.1-.664m-5.8 0A2.251 2.251 0 0 1 13.5 2.25H15c1.012 0 1.867.668 2.15 1.586m-5.8 0c-.376.023-.75.05-1.124.08C9.095 4.01 8.25 4.973 8.25 6.108V8.25m0 0H4.875c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h9.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V9.375c0-.621-.504-1.125-1.125-1.125H8.25ZM6.75 12h.008v.008H6.75V12Zm0 3h.008v.008H6.75V15Zm0 3h.008v.008H6.75V18Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Digital Records</h3>
          <p class="text-base-content/60">
            All contributions are stored securely. Never lose a register again.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 bg-base-200/50 border border-base-300">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-secondary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-secondary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 3 19.875v-6.75ZM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V8.625ZM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V4.125Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Analytics</h3>
          <p class="text-base-content/60">
            Real-time insights on contributions, totals, and guest participation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Company Info -->
    <div class="p-8 bg-base-200/50 border border-base-300 mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Company Information</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Business Name</h3>
          <p class="text-base-content/60">Moi</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Business Type</h3>
          <p class="text-base-content/60">Technology & Software Services</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Location</h3>
          <p class="text-base-content/60">India</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Contact</h3>
          <p class="text-base-content/60">
            <a href="mailto:abishek@merg.cc" class="text-primary hover:underline">abishek@merg.cc</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Mission Section -->
    <div class="p-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/5 to-secondary/5 border border-base-300 mb-16 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="text-base-content/60 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-6">
        To preserve and modernize cultural traditions by providing simple, accessible technology that brings families and communities together during life's most important celebrations.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <div class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to get started?</h2>
      <p class="text-base-content/60 mb-6">Create your first event in minutes</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/signup" class="px-8 py-4 bg-primary text-primary-content text-sm uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold hover:bg-primary/90 transition-all">
          Get Started
        </a>
        <a href="/support" class="px-8 py-4 border border-base-content/20 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest font-medium hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-colors">
          Contact Us
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</PageLayout>

